msgid "maxframe.learn.preprocessing.MinMaxScaler"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:1 of
msgid "Transform features by scaling each feature to a given range."
msgstr "通过将每个特征缩放到给定范围来转换特征。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:3 of
msgid ""
"This estimator scales and translates each feature individually such that "
"it is in the given range on the training set, e.g. between zero and one."
msgstr ""
"该估计器单独缩放和平移每个特征，使其在训练集上的取值处于给定范围内，例如"
"在0和1之间。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:7 of
msgid "The transformation is given by::"
msgstr "变换公式如下::"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:12 of
msgid "where min, max = feature_range."
msgstr "其中 min, max = feature_range。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:14 of
msgid ""
"This transformation is often used as an alternative to zero mean, unit "
"variance scaling."
msgstr "这种变换通常作为零均值、单位方差缩放的替代方法。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:17 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <preprocessing_scaler>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <preprocessing_scaler>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.MinMaxScaler.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:19 of
msgid "Desired range of transformed data."
msgstr "变换后数据的期望范围。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:21 of
msgid ""
"Set to False to perform inplace row normalization and avoid a copy (if "
"the input is already a numpy array)."
msgstr "设为 False 以执行原地行归一化并避免复制（如果输入已经是 numpy 数组）。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:24 of
msgid ""
"Set to True to clip transformed values of held-out data to provided "
"`feature range`."
msgstr "设为 True 以将保留数据的变换值裁剪到提供的 `feature range`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:30 of
msgid ""
"Per feature adjustment for minimum. Equivalent to ``min - X.min(axis=0) *"
" self.scale_``"
msgstr "每个特征的最小值调整。等价于 ``min - X.min(axis=0) * self.scale_``"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler of
msgid "type"
msgstr "类型"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:33
#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:40 of
msgid "Tensor of shape (n_features,)"
msgstr "形状为 (n_features,) 的张量"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:37 of
msgid ""
"Per feature relative scaling of the data. Equivalent to ``(max - min) / "
"(X.max(axis=0) - X.min(axis=0))``"
msgstr ""
"每个特征数据的相对缩放。等价于 ``(max - min) / (X.max(axis=0) - X.min("
"axis=0))``"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:44 of
msgid "Per feature minimum seen in the data"
msgstr "数据中每个特征的最小值"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:46
#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:52
#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:58 of
msgid "ndarray of shape (n_features,)"
msgstr "形状为 (n_features,) 的 ndarray"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:50 of
msgid "Per feature maximum seen in the data"
msgstr "数据中每个特征的最大值"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:56 of
msgid "Per feature range ``(data_max_ - data_min_)`` seen in the data"
msgstr "数据中每个特征的范围 ``(data_max_ - data_min_)``"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:62 of
msgid ""
"The number of samples processed by the estimator. It will be reset on new"
" calls to fit, but increments across ``partial_fit`` calls."
msgstr ""
"估计器处理的样本数。在新的 fit 调用时会重置，但在 ``partial_fit`` 调用"
"之间会递增。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:66 of
msgid "int"
msgstr "整数"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:69 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:87 of
msgid ":py:obj:`minmax_scale`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:88 of
msgid "Equivalent function without the estimator API."
msgstr "不使用估计器 API 的等效函数。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:91 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:92 of
msgid ""
"NaNs are treated as missing values: disregarded in fit, and maintained in"
" transform."
msgstr "NaN 被视为缺失值：在 fit 中忽略，在 transform 中保留。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.min_max_scaler.MinMaxScaler:95 of
msgid ""
"For a comparison of the different scalers, transformers, and normalizers,"
" see :ref:`examples/preprocessing/plot_all_scaling.py "
"<sphx_glr_auto_examples_preprocessing_plot_all_scaling.py>`."
msgstr ""
"有关不同缩放器、变换器和归一化器的比较，请参见 :ref:`examples/"
"preprocessing/plot_all_scaling.py <sphx_glr_auto_examples_preprocessing_"
"plot_all_scaling.py>`。"

